OL,3,CCharity director with terminal cancer
OL,4,Cawarded rare island honour
OL,6,FA charity director whose candid
OL,7,Freflections on his terminal cancer
OL,8,Fdiagnosis inspired people globally has
OL,9,Fbeen given a rare award.
OL,11,FSimon Boas wrote a series of articles
OL,12,Ffor a local newspaper detailing his
OL,13,Ftreatment and life that received
OL,14,Fhundreds of thousands of views online.
OL,16,FHe is also the Executive Director of
OL,17,FJersey Overseas Aid, the island's
OL,18,Fofficial humanitarian relief group,
OL,19,Fand holds a number of other voluntary
OL,20,Fpositions.
