OL,3,CCharity director with terminal cancer
OL,4,Cawarded rare island honour
OL,6,FIn a small private ceremony at his
OL,7,Fhome in Jersey, Simon was awarded the
OL,8,FSilver Seal by the Bailiff, Sir
OL,9,FTimothy Le Cocq.
OL,11,FPart of the inscription reads: "In
OL,12,Fparticular, during a time of great
OL,13,Fpersonal challenge he has continued to
OL,14,Foffer support and comfort to those in
OL,15,Fneed, both through his internationally
OL,16,Frecognised work and that of the
OL,17,Fvoluntary positions that he holds.
