OL,3,CCharity director with terminal cancer
OL,4,Cawarded rare island honour
OL,6,F"Furthermore, the words he has shared
OL,7,Fwith us all, reflecting on the beauty
OL,8,Fand wonder of life, have inspired
OL,9,Fhundreds of thousands of people around
OL,10,Fthe world."
OL,12,FSimon says: "I'm so delighted to be
OL,13,Fhonoured with this marvellous award.
OL,14,FNot only does it recognise the superb
OL,15,Forganisations with which I've been so
OL,16,Fprivileged to work and volunteer, but
OL,17,Fon a personal level it cements that
OL,18,Fwonderful feeling of acceptance and
OL,19,Fwelcome which Aurelie (Simon's wife)
OL,20,Fand I have always felt in Jersey.
