OL,3,CCharity director with terminal cancer
OL,4,Cawarded rare island honour
OL,6,F"It may not have been part of the plan
OL,7,Fthat I should die here, but I can't
OL,8,Fthink of a better soil in which to
OL,9,Frest."
OL,11,FThe Bailiff adds: "Simon has shown
OL,12,Fincredible strength at a time of
OL,13,Fpersonal challenge and his recent
OL,14,Fwritings have provided many with great
OL,15,Fcomfort and a sense of pride for the
OL,16,Fisland he now calls home."
